text: Andreina José Silva Encarnação (born 10 April 1993), known as Andreina Silva, is an Andorran footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Andorra women's national team. ==Career== Silva has been capped for the Andorra national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers
